vogar

Class AnnotatedOutcome

  • java.lang.Object
    • vogar.AnnotatedOutcome

  • public final class AnnotatedOutcome
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains an outcome for a test, along with some metadata pertaining to the history of this test, including a list of previous outcomes, an outcome corresponding to the tag Vogar is being run with, if applicable, and the expectation for this test, so that result value information is available.
